Summary: The UFO wAs a rectangular shape, with all sorts of different lights pulsating from it. It hovered in between my house and the neighbor s house for several minutes, before slowly heading south until it vanished.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was up at my usual 530 am. Just put coffee on the stove wen I noticed a cluster of lights,hovering just over my trees that separate us with our neighbor . At first it caught my eye,then I went back into kitchen, just then my husband had awoken off of couch facing porch window where object was in clear view. He then literally wiped his eyes and asked me if I had seen what he was witnessing. I said yes and we both observed the object hover for about 30 more second and started to slowly head south, my husband then ran out front of the house and watched the object fade out of view.
